- YEAH.

37:29.648 --> 37:31.950
- JUST BE CAREFUL.

37:38.924 --> 37:41.360
- LINDSAY.

37:41.393 --> 37:43.895
IT'S YOUR WEDDING PRESENT.

37:43.929 --> 37:47.766
