MAYBE SOMEDAY--

39:16.588 --> 39:17.889
- WHAT, YOU AND I?

39:17.923 --> 39:19.891
- YEAH, STRANGER THINGS
HAVE HAPPENED.

39:19.925 --> 39:21.427
- NOT REALLY.

39:21.460 --> 39:23.862
