A GOOD FUCKING ON THE BEACH.

39:23.895 --> 39:25.631
- HEY,

39:25.664 --> 39:27.566
I CAN'T GO.

39:27.599 --> 39:30.135
- YOU FORGOT
YOUR BAIN DE SOLEIL.

39:30.168 --> 39:32.738
- I WANT TO GO TO THE WEDDING.

39:32.771 --> 39:35.441
- FOR LINDSAY AND MELANIE?

39:35.474 --> 39:36.608
- FOR ME.

39:36.642 --> 39:38.444
I WANT TO BE A PART OF IT.

39:38.477 --> 39:41.747
